it must be important.

09:25.920 --> 09:28.080
-Shall we find somewhere to eat?
-Yeah, well, I...

09:28.160 --> 09:30.240
I got in touch 'cause I saw that
you were in town

09:30.320 --> 09:33.000
for what is it,
some, some architecture thing?

09:33.080 --> 09:34.720
It's a forum, they call it.

09:34.800 --> 09:37.320
People actually pay to come
and listen to me talk. [scoffs]

09:37.400 --> 09:38.280
Imagine that.

09:39.200 --> 09:40.880
