09:41.360 --> 09:43.520
And you're looking good.
Is that the gym?

09:43.600 --> 09:44.600
Well, you look--

09:44.680 --> 09:48.240
I look like dog shit, Mia.
I'll save you the bother.

09:48.560 --> 09:50.320
Dried-up dog shit.

09:50.400 --> 09:52.880
-[Mia] Do you want a drink?
-I knocked it on the head.

09:54.880 --> 09:56.480
What, you quit, like fully quit?

09:56.560 --> 09:59.480
[Rob] Nine months, three weeks, two days.

10:02.120 --> 10:04.440
Well done. Well, that's great.

10:04.520 --> 10:05.600
You go ahead.

10:06.600 --> 10:07.880
-Really, go on.
-You sure?

10:07.960 --> 10:10.080
-Absolutely.
-OK.

10:12.160 --> 10:15.960
[Mia] You picked a terrible place
to come see me 'cause it reeks of hops

10:16.040 --> 10:17.960
all the way down the street outside here.

10:18.040 --> 10:19.960
-Did you notice that?
-[Rob] No.

10:20.040 --> 10:23.400
-[Mia] It's like a full-on beer smell.
-[bottle opening, fizzing]

10:23.800 --> 10:25.440
