to hurt anyone else. What about me?

12:33.200 --> 12:34.800
-What about her?
-No, no, no.

12:36.320 --> 12:37.480
No.

12:40.560 --> 12:42.960
No! Fuck!

12:43.680 --> 12:45.640
[exhales, whimpers]

12:45.720 --> 12:48.120
It was your idea.
It was your fucking idea!

12:48.320 --> 12:52.760
