Think of him, please.

13:16.520 --> 13:17.520
I'm sorry.

13:21.200 --> 13:22.520
[Rob sighs]

13:23.680 --> 13:25.280
I sat on this for you.

13:25.360 --> 13:28.080
-I fucking sat on this for you!
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry!

13:33.120 --> 13:35.320
Hey, look at me.

13:35.400 --> 13:36.720
[sniffles]

