16:39.280 --> 16:42.080
-Happy birthday.
-Thanks.

16:44.360 --> 16:46.840
-[baby continues crying]
-[laughs]

16:48.560 --> 16:50.280
[squeaks]

16:54.000 --> 16:56.840
[clicks, bleeping]

16:59.680 --> 17:02.920
[police radio chatter]

17:03.000 --> 17:05.160
