-So you've got everything you needed?
-Yeah.

43:14.000 --> 43:16.600
Doesn't take long, it's just
a simple thing with the speed so...

43:16.680 --> 43:17.880
-[Mia] Right.
-Yeah. Yeah.

43:17.960 --> 43:20.760
[Mia] Sorry about being short,
it's been a long day.

43:20.840 --> 43:22.880
-No, it's fine.
-Got a lot of work on. Did you...

43:22.960 --> 43:25.880
-So you've got everything you needed?
-[Shazia] Yeah, yeah, got it all.

43:25.960 --> 43:28.360
-Don't worry, thank you so much.
-I know this sounds silly,

43:28.440 --> 43:33.160
but, um, you know, sometimes I just think
mad things, and it doesn't mean anything,

43:33.240 --> 43:35.880
do you know what I mean?
When you have strange thoughts.

43:35.960 --> 43:40.240
No, it's fine, like I said.
I got what I needed, so thank you.

43:40.320 --> 43:43.480
Yeah, but do you know what I mean?
It's not like... it's just my head.

43:48.280 --> 43:51.280
[car engine moans]

43:51.360 --> 43:52.600
[Shazia] Come on!

43:54.360 --> 43:55.400
[engine moans]

43:55.480 --> 43:56.600
No.

43:58.120 --> 44:01.040
[screaming] No, no, no, no! No!

44:01.120 --> 44:02.120
[Mia groans]

44:03.680 --> 44:04.880
[heavy breathing]

44:04.960 --> 44:06.200
[Shazia] No!

44:31.080 --> 44:33.240
[Mia] I'm sorry, um...

44:34.480 --> 44:37.320
-[Mia sniffles]
-[Shazia groaning]

44:37.680 --> 44:38.640
[Mia] Um...

44:40.360 --> 44:42.440
I fucked up, and I panicked.

44:44.680 --> 44:45.520
[Shazia whimpers]

44:51.720 --> 44:52.920
Does your head hurt?

44:57.960 --> 44:59.120
OK.

45:02.960 --> 45:03.800
[whimpers]

45:03.880 --> 45:04.880
[Mia] OK.

45:06.480 --> 45:08.480
[sobbing]

45:14.080 --> 45:15.840
What am I gonna do with you?

45:18.520 --> 45:20.680
[sobbing increases]

45:22.120 --> 45:23.960
I mean, I can't let you go.

45:25.720 --> 45:27.680
You're gonna tell someone, aren't you?

45:27.760 --> 45:28.680
[muffled sounds]

45:28.760 --> 45:32.480
I know, but even if you say you won't,
your recollections are all recorded.

45:32.560 --> 45:34.760
-[muffled] I won't.
-They're not?

45:34.840 --> 45:37.000
[Shazia sobbing] No.

45:37.840 --> 45:40.960
If I take that off your mouth,
will you promise not to scream?

45:41.040 --> 45:43.080
-Do you promise?
-[whimpers]

45:45.000 --> 45:48.720
Forget the report. I'll delete... [sniffs]
I'll delete it, it won't go anywhere.

45:48.800 --> 45:51.640
I don't know. I tried to delete it,
and I couldn't figure it out.

45:51.720 --> 45:54.600
I won't say anything to anyone, I promise.
I'll forget the whole thing.

45:54.680 --> 45:57.040
[crying] No one will know.
I won't say anything.

45:58.560 --> 45:59.880
I wish I believed you.

45:59.960 --> 46:03.880
I mean it. I mean it. I've seen things.

46:03.960 --> 46:05.520
I've seen things on the recaller.

46:06.240 --> 46:09.600
Secrets, personal things,
I've never spilled any of it.

46:09.680 --> 46:11.640
I'm not allowed to, it's the law.

46:11.720 --> 46:15.280
It's like confession,
it's like Catholic confession.

46:16.160 --> 46:20.480
It'll be illegal for me to say anything.
Totally illegal, even if I wanted to!

46:28.360 --> 46:29.480
None of that's true, is it?

46:29.560 --> 46:31.480
-It is, I swear.
-[Mia] It's not.

46:31.560 --> 46:32.800
It is.

46:34.120 --> 46:36.560
Did you tell anyone that
you were coming here today?

46:36.960 --> 46:37.960
No.

46:44.640 --> 46:48.120
-You're lying.
-I'm not. I swear I'm not lying.

46:48.200 --> 46:50.040
[Shazia sobs] No, I swear.

46:51.720 --> 46:53.560
[muffled] I swear. No!

46:53.640 --> 46:56.480
[gasps, screaming] No!

46:56.920 --> 46:57.880
No!

46:57.960 --> 47:00.360
[recaller fires up]

47:01.600 --> 47:07.120
-[bleeping]
-[Shazia moaning, sobbing]

47:10.320 --> 47:11.320
[ear piece bleeps]

47:13.400 --> 47:15.040
[sobbing] No!

47:16.440 --> 47:18.800
What did you do
before you came here today?

47:18.880 --> 47:22.560
-[Shazia crying]
-[static noise]

47:26.280 --> 47:29.400
[Shazia sings along to
"Anyone Who Knows What Love Is"]

47:30.160 --> 47:34.600
♪<i> Oh, but anyone ♪</i>

47:34.680 --> 47:36.640
♪<i> Who knows what love is... ♪</i>

47:36.720 --> 47:38.600
I like that song.

47:38.680 --> 47:42.600
-[Shazia sobbing]
-♪<i> Will understand ♪</i>

47:43.080 --> 47:44.400
Who did you speak to?

47:44.480 --> 47:45.880
[Shazia on video]<i> Bingo.</i>

47:46.640 --> 47:49.560
<i>-Mia Nolan, if she'll talk.</i>
-[Shazia continues sobbing]

47:49.640 --> 47:51.640
<i>-If she'll talk?</i>
-[Shazia] No!

47:57.720 --> 47:58.720
No.

48:02.880 --> 48:04.600
[Shazia whimpers]

48:04.680 --> 48:06.840
-Is that your husband?
-[muffled] No!

48:19.120 --> 48:20.680
[muffled sobbing] No!

48:20.760 --> 48:22.760
No!

48:26.120 --> 48:27.520
[Mia] I'm really sorry.

48:28.200 --> 48:30.720
[screaming] No!

48:33.040 --> 48:35.160
Will you please close your eyes for me?

48:38.440 --> 48:41.920
[Shazia utters muffled prayer]

48:45.600 --> 48:50.840
[banging, cracking]

48:59.520 --> 49:00.880
[whimpers]

49:03.560 --> 49:05.440
[retching]

49:24.240 --> 49:25.640
[keys jangle]

49:48.360 --> 49:50.040
[man]
<i>Everyone's in their costumes already.</i>

49:50.120 --> 49:51.760
<i>Yeah, please, make sure you're on time.</i>

49:51.840 --> 49:54.120
-Yeah, I know, love.
<i>-Are you far off?</i>

49:54.200 --> 49:58.000
<i>-Remember it starts at 7:30.</i>
-I'm gonna make it, 7:30.

49:58.080 --> 50:00.120
<i>-At 7:30.</i>
-Yeah. [sniffs]

50:00.200 --> 50:02.080
<i>-All right.</i>
-I'll see you outside.

50:02.160 --> 50:04.000
<i>-See you in a bit, sweetheart.</i>
-OK.

50:25.960 --> 50:28.320
[panting]

50:31.600 --> 50:34.280
[orchestral music playing]

50:37.840 --> 50:39.120
[door clicks open]

50:43.600 --> 50:44.600
[exhales]

50:47.800 --> 50:50.160
[orchestral music continues]

51:06.480 --> 51:07.320
[TV clicks off]

51:09.920 --> 51:10.880
[man clears throat]

51:12.160 --> 51:14.200
[door opens]

51:14.280 --> 51:16.560
[footsteps going upstairs]

51:20.360 --> 51:22.720
[footsteps]

51:29.440 --> 51:32.040
[water running]

51:45.720 --> 51:47.240
[water stops running]

51:50.320 --> 51:51.280
[water splashing]

51:53.080 --> 51:54.080
[sighs]

52:23.880 --> 52:26.120
[phone vibrating]

52:28.400 --> 52:29.720
[man gasps]

52:31.360 --> 52:32.560
[Mia groans]

52:32.640 --> 52:33.640
[thumps]

52:33.720 --> 52:35.640
[Mia panting]

52:40.880 --> 52:42.320
[Mia whimpers]

52:50.960 --> 52:53.640
[whimpering]

52:58.640 --> 53:00.720
[grunts, exhales]

53:06.400 --> 53:07.600
[crying]

53:21.800 --> 53:25.920
[baby coos, squealing]

53:30.800 --> 53:32.000
[baby babbling]

53:39.400 --> 53:42.160
[baby talk continues]

53:51.240 --> 53:53.920
[baby cries]

53:59.280 --> 54:01.200
[crying increases]

54:08.280 --> 54:11.360
[baby cooing, crying]

54:33.320 --> 54:36.320
-[man] Cutting it a bit fine.
-[Mia] Yeah, it was just work stuff.

54:37.840 --> 54:39.240
Jesus, what'd you eat, a vineyard?

54:39.320 --> 54:41.440
No, I just finished the design
so had a glass of wine.

54:41.520 --> 54:44.000
-[man] Fuck off, a glass. Fine.
-Let's just go in, all right?

54:44.600 --> 54:45.880
[man shivers]

54:45.960 --> 54:49.200
[piano playing]

54:51.400 --> 54:55.720
[piano continues]

55:03.720 --> 55:06.160
<i>♪ We coulda been anything ♪</i>

55:06.240 --> 55:10.360
<i>♪ That we wanted to be ♪</i>

55:11.600 --> 55:15.640
<i>♪ And it's not too late to change ♪</i>

55:18.560 --> 55:23.600
<i>♪ It's been decided</i>
<i>To give it some thought ♪</i>

55:25.040 --> 55:28.360
<i>♪ Maybe you'll agree we really ought ♪</i>

55:28.440 --> 55:30.560
<i>♪ Two, three, four! ♪</i>

55:31.000 --> 55:35.000
<i>♪ We coulda been anything</i>
<i>That we wanted to be ♪</i>

55:35.080 --> 55:35.920
[clapping to music]

55:36.000 --> 55:39.000
<i>♪ Yes, that decision was ours ♪</i>

55:41.160 --> 55:45.320
<i>♪ It's been decided we're weaker divided ♪</i>

55:46.000 --> 55:48.520
<i>♪ Let friendship double up our powers ♪</i>

55:48.600 --> 55:49.640
[sirens]

55:49.720 --> 55:52.200
[policeman over radio]
<i>Yeah, just confirming double homicide.</i>

55:52.280 --> 55:54.200
<i>One adult male and one male infant.</i>

55:55.120 --> 55:56.600
<i>Yeah, I'm at the scene now.</i>

55:56.680 --> 55:57.760
[sirens continue]

55:57.840 --> 56:00.040
-[camera shutter clicking]
-Who kills a baby?

56:04.280 --> 56:05.360
I don't know.

56:05.760 --> 56:08.040
Probably someone worried
about leaving a witness.

56:09.720 --> 56:12.480
[female detective]
Bloodbath upstairs and this downstairs.

56:13.160 --> 56:14.800
[male detective] But he couldn't see.

56:17.160 --> 56:19.200
Poor fucker was born blind apparently.

56:20.280 --> 56:23.440
So I have to say, I have absolutely
no idea who I'm looking for.

56:24.960 --> 56:27.360
So it's a good job you're not asking me.

56:31.960 --> 56:35.240
Come on, let's clear out of here.
Let's let the recall team do their job.

56:35.320 --> 56:37.400
-[camera clicking]
-[female detective] Come on.

56:37.480 --> 56:38.560
[guinea pig squeaking]

56:38.640 --> 56:40.080
[machine whirs]

56:40.160 --> 56:42.000
[forensic investigator] Here we go.

56:42.080 --> 56:44.040
-[guinea pig squeaks]
-[recaller beeps]

56:44.120 --> 56:47.160
[piano playing]

56:48.200 --> 56:52.280
<i>♪ You give a little love</i>
<i>And it all comes back to you ♪</i>

56:52.360 --> 56:55.440
<i>♪ La la la la la la la ♪</i>

56:55.520 --> 56:57.400
<i>♪ You know</i>
<i>You're gonna be remembered ♪</i>

56:57.480 --> 57:00.600
<i>♪ For the things that you say and do ♪</i>

57:00.680 --> 57:03.400
[cheering, applause]

57:03.480 --> 57:04.600
[mother] Well done!

57:04.680 --> 57:07.800
[teacher] Put your hands together
for this year's fantastic school choir.

57:07.880 --> 57:11.160
What a lovely evening.
Thank you so much for coming.

57:17.920 --> 57:20.680
Put your hands together
for Mrs. Henry...

57:21.920 --> 57:25.720
[mother] Bravo! Yay!
